cc:Work.dc:title: Dream of Escape
cc:Work.dc:description: Expert from a dream I had the other day

flowRoot.flowPara: From one prison to another maybe transferring from one to another every so often can save I from these unfortunate feelings of sadness and lack of motivation to accomplish what I want.

text.tspan: The desire to find joy within creativity
I should keep it to myself
From the comfort of my bed
sucking me into a land where
your mind runs free and life materializes
